  topCode: "#include<iostream>\r\n\r#include<tcgaddon.h>\nusing namespace std;\r\n\r\nint
    main(int argc,char * argv[]){\r\n  const int code = 32;\r\n  int counter=0;\r\n 
    int secretNumbers[argc-1];\n\n  readArray(argc,argv,secretNumbers);\n\n\t\n/*\r\n 
    For every secret number check if it is greater or equal to code variable,\r\n 
    and if it is, increase counter variable by 1, and display that secret number
    (display all numbers in new lines)\r\n\r\n  After for loop display counter value.\r\n\r\n 
    Example:\r\n  secretNumbers = {0,32,12,34,76,10};\r\n\r\n  output:\r\n  32\r\n 
    34\r\n  76\r\n  3\r\n  \r\n*/"
